name: Tracking Shipment
query:
SELECT `tabMaterial Request Item`.parent as "Name:Link/Material Request:150", `tabMaterial Request Item`.item_code as "Item Code:Data:150", `tabMaterial Request Item`.description as "Description:Data:150", `tabMaterial Request Item`.technical_description as "Technical Description:Data:150", `tabMaterial Request Item`.qty as "Qty:Data:50", `tabMaterial Request Item`.uom as "UOM:Data:80", `tabDelivery Note Item`.parent as "Delivery Note Reference:Data:80", `tabDelivery Note Item`.qty as "DC Qty:Data:80", `tabDelivery Note Item`.uom as "DC UOM:Data:80", CASE WHEN `tabDelivery Note Item`.parent IS NOT NULL THEN "

Delivered

" ELSE "

Not Delivered

" END as "Status:HTML:100" FROM `tabMaterial Request Item` LEFT OUTER JOIN `tabDelivery Note Item` ON `tabMaterial Request Item`.name=`tabDelivery Note Item`.material_request_item WHERE `tabMaterial Request Item`.docstatus=1 and `tabMaterial Request Item`.`project`=%(project)s
